1. Install React:

npm i react react-dom
2. Install Webpack:

npm i webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server
3. Install the babel loaders for Webpack to use:

npm i babel-loader@7 babel-core babel-preset-env babel-preset-react
4. Create a .babelrc file:

{
    "presets" ["babel-preset-env", "babel-preset-react"]
}
5. Create the webpack.config.js file.

6. Create your src/public folders and start writing your source code for React.